\id 1TH 1TƐ - Bible Iyansi 
\h 1 TƐSALƆNIKÀ 
\toc1 Un'kaan atàtwɛb akà Atɛsalɔnikà 
\toc2 1 TƐSALƆNIKÀ 
\toc3 1Tɛ 
\mt2 Un'kaan atàtwɛb akà 
\mt1 Atɛsalɔnikà 
\imt1 Nsɛmà 
\ip Un'kaan wàtàtwɛb awà akà aklistɔ a Ikööŋ a Tɛsalɔnikà, làbuŋ a Masɛdwan, amu ɛwà Ɛzɛ, ntööm Pɔl kàsön unsà un'tüüb anà Silavɛ anà Tumatɛ. U tàtwɛb, Pɔl kàlɔŋ baar a Tɛsalɔnikà mutiin inswem, mukal anà ukwen ba a ba, musal ntɔn indiir aba byà mfun. Ungö, nde kàbaal naa baar in'kyɛɛl bàfàkwà kusà a mfurà a Mwol bàyapiy anki, ba bàkyer asàwiyà uboo akü utaaŋ usàmɛnà Klistɔ kusà a Mwol a imwol ande kyanswà. Nde kayɔɔb sye naa Yɛsu asàyà kà imburà, wɛɛ ba twon ban'kal u nkyɛl. U ntsüü, nde kabaal naa mɔ̈ɔ̈ aba uboo a Ikööŋ akal aben. Kiin a ndaa kàtɛn Pɔl akà ba yà naa: « Bɛ, làläb isal abɛ. » 
\ie  
\c 1  
\s1 Mbɔr 
\p  
\v 1 Mɛ Pɔl, Silàvɛ anà Tumàtɛ. 
\p Bi ban'pà mbɔr akà Ikööŋ a Atɛsalɔnikà akyà kyà Taa Nzam, anà kyà Mwol Yɛsu Klistɔ, wɛy kab a ngway anà duu màkäl anà bɛ. 
\s1 Mɔ̈ɔ̈ anà làkwikilà a Atɛsalɔnikà 
\p  
\v 2 Bi ifàyɔn anki mufuur an'tɔɔn akà Nzam ntɔn bɛ banswà mpal ifàlatà bi din uboo a ngyamàkà abi.  
\v 3 Bi ifàyɔbà kusà a Taaràbi Nzam isal ufàtwey nde làkwikilà abɛ, akyà ukwen abɛ, anà kyà muküünà ifàfà unsà làkyän abɛ amu Mwol abi Yɛsu Klistɔ.  
\v 4 Bi ikyàyöb, atɔŋ ukwen Nzam, naa nde kàlasɔ̈ɔ̈l.  
\v 5 Ntɔn, mpal kàlakyään bi Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ, làkäl anki u ndaa mpɛl, wɛɛ sye unsà ngwal a Dweelà In'kyɛɛl, anà kam aŋàkwo. Bɛ làkyàyöb naa ifà abi byàkäl aben uboo a bɛ, ntɔn ubwaŋ abɛ.  
\v 6 Apan bɛ, bɛ làläb nkääl abi anà yà Mwol, mukyey Ndaa uboo mpay aŋàdiir, anà un'sak kan'fà akà Dweelà In'kyɛɛl.  
\v 7 Abun, bɛ làkyàbulà mbaan ntɔn aŋàlàkwikilà banswà u bul a Masɛdwan anà Akayi.  
\v 8 Kyakin, fà akà bɛ, kà nà ndaa a Mwol mpɛl anki yàpää amu Masɛdwan anà amu Akayi, wɛɛ anà làsaŋ a làkwikilà abɛ amu Nzam làkyer apää ntsü yanswà, waa bi undiir afàtɛn watɛy.  
\v 9 Ntɔn ba ŋakwo bàmutà imbäl naa bɛ bi liwɛl abɛn mpal kàyi bi akà bɛ, anà bɛ làwɛy abɛn itɛk ntɔn musyääl Nzam a mɔ̈ɔ̈ anà wàndandaa,  
\v 10 anà làdilà Mwan ande kan'fà du, Nde akwà kàwiyà uboo a akü, Yɛsu awà kitsuuŋà u nkyɛl a Nzam ayà tsütsü muyà. 
\c 2  
\s1 Isal a Pɔl u Tɛsalɔnikà 
\p  
\v 1 Atɔŋ, bɛ ŋakwo làkyayöb naa ngyeel abi akà bɛ kà yàkäl yà bunàbun anki.  
\v 2 Wɛɛ, ungö mukipà mpay anà mukito u bul a Filipe, asànaa làyɔb bɛ, Nzam kipɛ ngwal mukàlakyään Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ ande, uboo a ngwiy a kölàköl.  
\v 3 Ntɔn, ndɛɛl abi kàyàŋàbwaay anki udu a ndiimà, itàkal udu a an'kyän a ŋingyay, itàkal u mbwo a an'kyän a loor.  
\v 4 Wɛɛ Nzam kàkyisyeebà anà kàkyiman bàŋàkwo mukyään Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ, kyakin bi ya ifàkyään anki ntɔn mupà un'sak akà baar, wɛɛ akà Nzam awafàler mpem abi.  
\v 5 Kyakin, bɛ làkyàyöb, Nzam wà mbäl abi, naa bi kàsyääl anki akà ikikye ndaa alwab baar, itàkal an'kyän muwal bweel.  
\v 6 Bi kàleŋ anki làkoo a baar, itàkal akà bɛ, itàkal akà bumwɛy,  
\v 7 itàkal naa bi ibà antööm a Klistɔ, bi kàlàsiinà anki a ngwal mukal ungyɛl a ikɔ̈b abi. Wɛɛ bi bàkäl aŋàyɔl a làbɔ̈ɔ̈n uboo a bɛ, asànaa maa ufàbööb nde baan ande.  
\v 8 Ntɔn bi kàkäl anà ukwen mbɔɔn akà bɛ, bi kàmɛn naa yà ubwaŋ bi kàlapɛ kà nà Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ a Nzam mpɛl anki, wɛɛ anà mɔ̈ɔ̈ abi ŋakwo, ntɔn bɛ làbà bàntal akà bi.  
\v 9 Atɔŋ, bɛ làkyàkayɔbà mpay anà yɔ̈ɔ̈n abi: bi kàsälà mpib anà mwäänà ntɔn mukɔɔn akal buur akà umwɛy ubɔɔ abɛ, waa bi kàlakyään Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ a Nzam.  
\v 10 Bɛ làbà ambäl anà Nzam sye: nkääl abi kusà a bɛ, aŋàlàkwikilà, yàkäl yà in'kyɛɛl, yàbalàbal, ikɔ̈ɔ̈n an'pɛl.  
\v 11 Bɛ làkyàyöb naa bi bàkyerà aben akà umwɛy umwey uboo a bɛ. Bi kàkyer asànaa taa anà baan ande ŋakwo,  
\v 12 mukàlalɛɛl, mukàlapà ngwal, anà mukàlalɔ̈ɔ̈m mukal anà nkääl aŋàkwo a Nzam awà kàlabel u Imwol ande anà u làkoo ande. 
\p  
\v 13 Kyakin, akà bi, bi ifàfuur an'tɔɔn akà Nzam taaŋ lanswà: mpal bàlakyään bi ndaa a Nzam, bɛ làkyer awem anà làkyey ya, kà asànaa ndaa a mbuur anki, wɛɛ asànaa ndaa a Nzam, ntɔn ya yà ndandaa. Kyakin, ya ifàsal ngwal amu bɛ aŋàlàkwikilà.  
\v 14 Atɔŋ, bɛ làyweel Ikööŋ a Nzam abyà u Yuday, amu Klistɔ Yɛsu. Ntɔn mpay nsil ya làmɛn bɛ akà atɔŋ abɛ ŋakwo, ba sye bàmɛn ya akà Ayudà.  
\v 15 Ba bà baar bàdwä Mwol Yɛsu anà aŋangɔɔm, anà bimɛɛy nkwaaŋ. Nzam un'sak watɛy anà ba. Ba bàŋankir a baar banswà!  
\v 16 Ba bàfàkyer ngwal mukidüüb mbwo muyääm anà baar mpa abà Ayudà manà naa ba bàwü mɔ̈ɔ̈. Abun, ba bàmukwɛy man'be udu a man'be aba taaŋ lanswà, anà u ngöngö, nkyɛl a Nzam ikyer asabweel. 
\s1 Pɔl akwen mufàman baar a Tɛsalɔnikà 
\p  
\v 17 Wɛɛ akà bi, atɔŋ, bi kàkyer akaabà anà bɛ taaŋ làmwɛy, itàkal naa bi ifàmɛɛn anki, bɛ làbà u mpem abi. Bi kàkäl anà ilɛɛm mukàlaman, anà bi kàkyer ngwal mbɔɔn mukwey ya.  
\v 18 Bi kàkwen muyà akà bɛ: mɛ ŋakwo, Pɔl, kàsi mbalà mbɔɔn. Wɛɛ Satanà laa kidüüb nde mbwo.  
\v 19 Abun, nà, isàkal naa kà bɛ anki, abà làkyän abi, un'sak abi, anà ngaal isàkal mpà a làkoo abi kusà a Mwol Yɛsu umpal usàyà nde?  
\v 20 Ɛɛ, bɛ làbà làkoo anà un'sak abi. 
\c 3  
\p  
\v 1 Kyakin, bi kàkwe anki mukaŋ mpem, waa bàyweer naa yubwaŋ bi isàsal bi mpɛl u bul a Atɛn.  
\v 2 Bi kàmàlatööm un'tɔŋ abi Tumàtɛ, mbaay abi unsà isal a Làsaŋ Aŋàbwaŋ a Klistɔ, ntɔn mukàlalɛɛl anà mukàlapà ngwal unsà làkwikilà abɛ,  
\v 3 ntɔn, akumwɛy uboo a bɛ ukɔɔn akwɛlà unsà mpay aŋàdiir yi. Ntɔn bɛ làkyàyöb bɛ ŋakwo naa bi bibel ntɔn mpay ayi.  
\v 4 Mpal kàkäl bi apà bɛ, bi kàlaweey naa bi bàkyer asimɛɛy nkwaaŋ. Abun ya sye yan'mɛnà asànaa làyöb bɛ ya ubwaŋàbwaŋ.  
\v 5 Asànaa mɛ kàfàkwo anki mukaŋ mpem, mɛ kàtöm Tumàtɛ ntɔn muyöb naa làkwikilà abɛ là aben. Bɔɔmà amɛ làkäl naa manà Un'lwɛb kàlalwɛb, anà isal kàkyer bi ikyà bwà.  
\v 6 Apà, Tumàtɛ kan'yàfurà kàfü nde akà bɛ, anà kàmipà làsaŋ aŋàbwaŋ là làkwikilà abɛ anà lukwen abɛ. Nde kan'tɛn naa bɛ làfàyɔbà bi taaŋ lanswà anà làbà anà ngyal mufiman asànaa ibà bi sye anà ngyal mukàlaman.  
\v 7 Apan, atɔŋ, bi kan'wal ndɛɛl amu bɛ, u mbwo a làkwikilà abɛ, uboo a ngyɛb aŋàdiir abi yanswà anà mpay abi.  
\v 8 Apanà, bi kan'fàyaabà, ntɔn bɛ làbà aŋàtsim unsà un'tüüb abɛ anà Mwol.  
\v 9 Bi Nzam abi ifun'kömà aben u ndaa abɛ, ntɔn un'sak wanswà làmipà bɛ kusà ande?  
\v 10 Mpib anà mwäänà, bi ifàlɔm akà nde unsà muküünà ntɔn nde kipɛ mbwo mufàlaman anà mukwɛy undiir akɔ̈ɔ̈n u làkwikilà abɛ. 
\p  
\v 11 Wɛy Nzam nde ŋakwo, anà Mwol Yɛsu biduub mbwo muyà akà bɛ!  
\v 12 Wɛy Mwol uyɛɛl anà ukwɛy ukwen làbà bɛ abà bɛ a bɛ anà akà baar banswà, asànaa ifàlakwen bi.  
\v 13 Wɛy nde upɛ ngwal u mpem abɛ, ntɔn wa ukäl win'kyɛɛl anà wàbalàbal kusà a Taaràbi Nzam, umpal usàyà Mwol abi Yɛsu anà aŋin'kyɛɛl ande banswà. Wöwöö. 
\c 4  
\s1 Un'kyɛɛl uboo Ikööŋ 
\p  
\v 1 Abun, atɔŋ, bɛ làkyer alɔŋàkà akà bi naa nkääl abɛ ikal aben mupà Nzam un'sak, bɛ sye làfàkyer abun. Apanà, bi kàmàlalɔɔm anà kàmàlalɛɛl kikɔb a Mwol Yɛsu, fàlakyerà yàŋàsöönà.  
\v 2 Ntɔn, bɛ làkyàyöb nswɛɛŋ kàlapɛ bi, nswɛŋ yàfü akà Mwol Yɛsu.  
\v 3 Ukwen a Nzam bà naa bɛ làbulà aŋin'kyɛɛl: wɛy bɛ làtön induumà.  
\v 4 Wɛy umwɛy umwɛy uboo a bɛ uyöb muwal un'kaar unsà un'kyɛɛl anà ibyääl,  
\v 5 ntɔn mukɔɔn akal ungyɛl a ikɔ̈b a làmfɛɛl asànaa bàfàkyer baar mpa abà Ayudà mpa bàyöb Nzam.  
\v 6 Unsà ndaa ayi, wɛy mbuur ukɔɔn akyer un'tɔŋ ande ube anà akɔɔn akun'kur, ntɔn Mwol afàpà ntaaŋàmbar unsà indiir abi byanswà, asànaa kàtɛn bi anà kàlaweey bi itaan.  
\v 7 Ntɔn Nzam kibeel anki ntɔn bi ikäl uboo a ŋingyäy, wɛɛ kibeel mukal uboo a un'kyɛɛl.  
\v 8 Kyakin, mbuur apiy nswɛɛŋ ayi, kà mbuur anki nde kan'piy, wɛɛ Nzam, Nde awà afàlapà Dweelà In'kyɛɛl ande. 
\p  
\v 9 Ntɔn ukwen a atɔŋ anà atɔŋ, mfun mukàlasöön yatɛy, ntɔn bɛ ŋakwo Nzam kàkyàlalɔŋ naa bɛ làkal anà ukwen bɛ a bɛ.  
\v 10 Anà bɛ làfàkyer abun akà atɔŋ banswà u bul a Masɛdwan lanswà. Atɔŋ, bi kàmàlalɛɛl, fàlakyerà yàŋàsöönà!  
\v 11 Làkäl anà ngyal mukal anà mɔ̈ɔ̈ a duu: wɛy mbuur mbuur ukyer indiir ande ŋakwo anà udi mbɛŋ a isal a an'kɔɔ ande ŋakwo, asànaa kàlaswɛŋ bi.  
\v 12 Abun, nkääl abɛ iyàkal yibyääl kusà a baar mpa abà aklistɔ, waa bɛ mpa làyàkal anà mfun a mbuur. 
\s1 Ngyeel a Mwol 
\p  
\v 13 Atɔŋ, bi ikwen naa bɛ làyöb ndandaa ntɔn akü, ntɔn bɛ làkɔɔn akal u ngyɛb asànaa baar bumwɛy bàkɔ̈ɔ̈n làkyän.  
\v 14 Ntɔn, isàkal naa bi ibye anà làkwikilà naa Yɛsu kàkyàkwà anà kàkyàwiyà, bi kan'sà làkwikilà sye naa Nzam, u mbwo a Yɛsu, asàsyen baar bàkü amu Yɛsu.  
\v 15 Le, undiir itɛɛnà bi a bɛ kan'fà u Ndaa a Mwol: baar bàsàkal anà mɔ̈ɔ̈ uboo a bi umpal usàyà Mwol, bàsàfwel anki baar bàkü.  
\v 16 Ntɔn nde ŋakwo, Mwol, u ndaa a ngwal anà u ndaa a mfum a akyeey, anà say a mfuŋ a Nzam, Mwol ŋakwo asyetyà fà du, baar bàkü amu Klistɔ bàsàwiyà bàtàtwɛb,  
\v 17 ungö, bi baar a mɔ̈ɔ̈ abà isàsaal, Nzam asisɛɛn anà ba uboo a itööm, ntɔn mukàbwey anà Mwol u du. Abun bi isàkal ipepey anà Mwol.  
\v 18 Làlɛɛl bɛ a bɛ u mbwo a ndaa ayi. 
\c 5  
\p  
\v 1 Atɔŋ, ntɔn an'taaŋ anà ilä, mfun mukàlasɔ̈ɔ̈n yatɛy.  
\v 2 Ntɔn bɛ ŋakwo làkyàyöb ubwaŋàbwaŋ naa ilä a Mwol isàyà asànaa mbüüb uboo a mpib.  
\v 3 Mpal bàsàtɛn baar naa: « Ɔɔ, indiir byanswà abyà u du, byà kà ikyɛɛŋ! », apan, kà imbürà, ibaŋ a mpay isàbwà udu a ba asànaa in'swaŋ udu a un'kaar aŋayöm. Akà mbuur mwɛy usàsɔrà anki.  
\v 4 Wɛɛ bɛ, atɔŋ, bɛ kàlàbà uboo a làpib anki, waa ilä iyàlataan asànaa mbüüb.  
\v 5 Ntɔn bɛ banswà làbà baan a pɛɛlà, baan a mwäänà: bi kibà baar a mpib anki, itàkal bà làpib anki.  
\v 6 Kyakin, wɛy bi ikɔɔn abɔ̈ɔ̈n asànaa baar bumwɛy, wɛɛ bi ikal kigyɛɛŋ anà u làbɔ̈ɔ̈n.  
\v 7 Baar bàfàbɔ̈ɔ̈n, bàfàbɔ̈ɔ̈n u mpib, in'nweel a man, bàfàyɔr u mpib.  
\v 8 Ntɔn bi ibà baan a mwäänà, bi ikal bàlàbɔ̈ɔ̈n, bàŋàbwaar làkwikilà anà ukwen asànaa kàzak ibeenà, anà làkyän a mɔ̈ɔ̈ asànaa mpà ibeenà.  
\v 9 Ntɔn Nzam kisɔ̈ɔ̈l anki naa nkyɛl ande yibweel, wɛɛ muwà mɔ̈ɔ̈ u mbwo a Mwol abi Yɛsu Klistɔ,  
\v 10 awà kàkü ntɔn bi, ntɔn itàkal bàmɔ̈ɔ̈ itàkal bàŋàkwà, bi ibilà mbwo mwɛy anà nde, uboo a mɔ̈ɔ̈.  
\v 11 Kyakin, làlɛɛl bɛ a bɛ anà làpɛɛl ngwal bɛ a bɛ, asànaa làfàtàkyer bɛ. 
\p  
\v 12 Atɔŋ, bi kàmàlalɔɔm mukan baar bàfàsal uboo a bɛ, baar, unsà ukwen a Mwol, bàfàlaler anà bàfàlaweey.  
\v 13 Lapɛ làzir anà ukwen, ntɔn isal aba. Làkäl a duu uboo a bɛ. 
\p  
\v 14 Atɔŋ, bi kàmàlalɛɛl, làweey aŋunkwɛm, làpɛ ngwal akà baar aŋàyɔn, làbay aŋagyɔ̈ɔ̈là, làkäŋ mpem akà baar banswà.  
\v 15 Làkäl kikyɛɛŋ, wɛy mbuur ukɔɔn afuur ube unsà ube, wɛɛ taaŋ lanswà làkyer ubwaŋ uboo a bɛ anà akà baar banswà. 
\p  
\v 16 Làkäl kun'sak taaŋ lanswà.  
\v 17 Làyamà ukɔɔn ayɔn.  
\v 18 Làfuur an'tɔɔn akà Nzam unsà ndaa yanswà, ntɔn ba ukwen ande akà bɛ amu Klistɔ Yɛsu. 
\p  
\v 19 Twon lan'düüb mbwo a isal a Dweelà In'kyɛɛl,  
\v 20 twon lan'bɛy ndaa a aŋangɔɔm,  
\v 21 wɛɛ làsyeebà indiir byanswà: làkäär yàŋabwaŋ,  
\v 22 làtön yàmbe yanswà. 
\p  
\v 23 Wɛy nde ŋakwo Nzam a duu kàlabuul bàŋukiinà aŋin'kyɛɛl, wɛy dweelà abɛ, mɔ̈ɔ̈ abɛ anà ndür abɛ byàkäl byàŋàtii ubwaŋàbwaŋ, ntɔn bya ikɔ̈ɔ̈n akal anà an'pɛl umpal usàyà Mwol abi Yɛsu Klistɔ.  
\v 24 Nde mbuur kàlabel wà lää, nde mbuur asàkwey ya.  
\v 25 Atɔŋ, làyàmà sye ntɔn bi.  
\v 26 Lapɛ atɔŋ banswà mbɔr u mbwo a ndüür a itɔŋ.  
\v 27 Mɛ amàlabɔɔn kikɔb a Mwol: làtäŋ un'kaan wà akà atɔŋ banswà. 
\p  
\v 28 Wɛy kab a ngway a Mwol abi Yɛsu Klistɔ làkäl anà bɛ.